lead_paragraph: Seattle Seahawks wide receiver Tyler Lockett needed lengthy surgery after suffering a badly broken leg on Saturday, said head coach Peter Carroll.

headline.print_headline: Seattle's Lockett Needed Lengthy Surgery on Broken Leg
